OL,3,CFire breaks out at popular 300-year-
OL,4,Cold Welsh pub
OL,6,FFire crews are at the scene of a fire
OL,7,Fwhich has broken out at a 300-year-old
OL,8,FWelsh pub on Thursday morning.
OL,10,FA number of fire engines have been
OL,11,Fpictured at the Hare & Hounds pub in
OL,12,FAberthin, Cowbridge.
OL,14,FThe pub reopened in early 2015 when
OL,15,Flocal chef Tom Watts-Jones and his
OL,16,Fwife, Sarah, took over and renovated
OL,17,Fthe site.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
