OL,3,CFire breaks out at popular 300-year-
OL,4,Cold Welsh pub
OL,6,FSouth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,7,Fsaid it received a call at around
OL,8,F8.30am to reports of a fire at a
OL,9,Fproperty on Maendy Road, Aberthin.
OL,11,FA spokesperson from South Wales Police
OL,12,Fsaid: "Please avoid the area and use
OL,13,Falternative routes where possible.
OL,14,FThank you for your patience."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
