OL,3,CFire breaks out at popular 300-year-
OL,4,Cold Welsh pub
OL,6,FA fire service spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Crews, appliances, a water bowser,
OL,8,Fand an aerial hydraulic platform from
OL,9,FBridgend, Llantwit Major, Barry,
OL,10,FPontypridd, Kenfig Hill and Ely are
OL,11,Fcurrently in attendance. The incident
OL,12,Fis on-going."
